            , we are varnish makers, and live in Little Queen-street. The prisoner had been in our service, but was not so on the 5th of January. He was frequently sent to Messrs. Burgess, while with us. He has left us about three years; I never sent him there on the 5th of January; the order was not sent from our house. It is the prisoner's writing, I believe.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. It is not my writing.</p>
